main_body:
In the first paragraph of Article 9 of Regulation (EC) No 174/1999, points (a), (b), (c) and (d) are replaced by the following:
‘(a) 15 % for products covered by CN code 0405;
(b) 15 % for products covered by CN code 0402 10;
(c) 15 % for products covered by CN code 0406;
(d) 15 % for other products.’
